{"tid":1991164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[討論捉鬼論]唔捉鬼代唔代表唔防身邊有鬼？","createTime":"2020-04-27T08:50:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T09:44:33.000Z","uid":41389,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0fccf90aa557bae462a5ede3981db162c3fca75c","tid":1991164,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T08:50:48.000Z","msg":"開始有狗隻帶風向講到有人叫手足報名聯絡之前質疑下人地都叫捉鬼<br />\n<br />\n捉鬼係唔岩 但保護自己呢啲條件反射係一定要有<br />\n<br />\n正如你會唔會比你身份證比街邊一個連佢係乜水都唔知既人<br />\n<br />\n捉鬼搞到唔係鬼既手足出曬事 係絕對唔可以鼓吹<br />\n<br />\n但如果見到一個陷阱提手足唔好踩落去 大家分析下 我覺得係必要<br />\n<br />\n你知tg group 唔知有幾多狗account混左入去 <br />\n<br />\n之前老豆搵仔又show左個出賣手足既人 <br />\n<br />\n如果唔防身邊人 會好危險 自己位置 身份 小隊資料呢啲野 唔亂比人呢啲防人之心 唔叫做捉鬼<br />\n<br />\n同埋 唔通一隻便衣卧底狗跌埋委任證出黎都叫唔好捉鬼唔好搞佢？"},{"pid":"68e6c8d1b67d81fded1d70a4bbe717fdd4934df9","tid":1991164,"uid":286685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T08:53:52.000Z","msg":"諗起呢條仆街<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hJzOLFN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhJzOLFN.jpg&h=f33c1b8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gknwJsu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgknwJsu.jpg&h=e7e8fb27&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a279bb21b009f2ce9ebc75f3325b1820b02d8b97","tid":1991164,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68e6c8d1b67d81fded1d70a4bbe717fdd4934df9","tid":1991164,"uid":286685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T08:53:52.000Z","msg":"諗起呢條仆街<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hJzOLFN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhJzOLFN.jpg&h=f33c1b8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gknwJsu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgknwJsu.jpg&h=e7e8fb27&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T08:56:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass